<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n53115d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53115d">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53115d"> 115(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> a jesuit tale of the times</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">HARDY, ELIZABETH, novelist; b. Ireland, 1794; wrote <cite>Michael Cassidy</cite>, 1840; <mark><cite>The Confessor: a Jesuit Tale of the Times</cite></mark>, 1851, and many others of a like tendency, all anonymous; was confined in Queen&apos;s Bench prison, London, for a small debt, and after lingering a year and a half, d. there, 1854. <small> John S. Crone, <a name="JSCD1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JSCD1"><cite title="source">A Concise Dictionary of Irish Biography</cite></a> (Apr 1928) 89</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
